hadiths[53]{hadithnumber,text}:
2637,"jab un par tohmat lagaaney walon ne tohmat lagai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali aur Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni biwi (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu)) ko apne se juda karne ke mutaalliq mashwara karne ke liye bulaayaa, kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ab tak (is silsiley mein) wahi nahi aai thi. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne to ye kaha ke aap ki paak bevi ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( mein ham siwaey khair ke aur kuchh nahi jantey aur Barira (Raziallahu anhu) (unki khaadima ( ne kaha ke main koi aisi cheez nahi janti jis se un par aib lagaya ja sakey. itni baat zaroor hai ke wo nau-umr ladki hain ke aata goondhtii aur phir ja ke so rehti hai aur bakri aa kar usey kha leti hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (tohmat ke jhoot Sabit honey ke baad) farmaya ke aisey shakhs ki taraf se kon maafi talab karega jo meri biwi ke barey mein bhi mujhey takleef pahunchata hai. qism Allah ki! maine apne ghar mein khair ke siwa aur kuchh nahi dekha aur log aisey shakhs ka naam letey hain jiske mutaalliq bhi mujhey khair ke siwa aur kuchh malum nahi."
2638,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ubai-bin-Kab Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar khajoor ke us baagh ki taraf tashrif le gaey jis mein ibne-Sayyaad tha. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baagh mein dakhil huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darakhton ki aad mein chhup kar chalney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chahtey they ke ibne-Sayyaad aapko dekhney na paaey aur us se pahley aap uski baatein sun sakein. ibne-Sayyaad aik ro'ein-daar chadar mein zameen par leta hua tha aur kuchh gungunaa raha tha. ibne-Sayyaad ki maan ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh liya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darakht ki aad liye chaley aa rahe hain to wo kehney lagi aey Saaf! ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aa rahe hain. ibne-Sayyaad hoshiyaar ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar usey apne haal par rehney deti to baat zahir ho jaatii.''
2639,"main Rifaa ke nikah mein thi. phir mujhey unhon-ne talaaq de di aur qatae talaaq de di. phir maine Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se shadi kar li. lekin unke paas to (sharmgaah) us kapdey ki gaanth ki tarah hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum kya ''kya to Rifaa ke paas dobara jana chahti hai lekin to us waqt tak unse ab shadi nahi kar sakti jab tak to Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Zubair ka mazaa na chakh ley aur wo tumhara mazaa na chakh lein.'' us waqt Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khidmate-nabawii mein maujood they aur Khaalid-bin-Saeed-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) darwazey par apne liye (andar aaney ki) ijazat ka intizar kar rahe they. unhon-ne kaha, abu-Bakar! kya us aurat ko nahi dekhtey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kis tarah ki baatein zor-zor se keh rahi hai."
2640,"unhon-ne Abu-Abaab-bin-Azeez ki ladki se shadi ki thi. aik khatun aaiin aur kehney lagiin ke Aqba ko bhi maine doodh pilaya hai aur usey bhi jis se us ne shadi ki hai. Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey to malum nahi ke aap ne mujhey doodh pilaya hai aur aap ne mujhey pahley is silsiley mein kuchh bataya bhi nahi tha. phir unhon-ne aal-Abu-Abaab ke yahan aadmi bheja ke unse iske mutaalliq poochhey. unhon-ne bhi yahi jawab diya ke hamein malum nahi ke unhon-ne doodh pilaya hai. Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Madina hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se masla poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ab kya ho sakta hai jabke kaha ja chukaa. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon mein judai kara di aur iska nikah doosrey shakhs se kara diya."
2641,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein logon ka wahi ke zariey muaakhza ho jata tha. lekin ab wahiy ka silsila khatm ho gaya aur ham sirf unhiin maamlon mein poochh-gachh karengey jo tumharey amal se hamarey samney zahir hongey. isliye jo koi zahir mein hamarey samney khair karega, ham usey amn dengey aur apne qareeb rakhengey. iske baatin se hamein koi sarokaar na hoga. iska hisab to Allah Taala karega aur jo koi hamarey samney zahir mein burai karega to ham bhi usey amn nahi dengey aur na ham uski tasdeeq karengey chahe wo yahi kehta rahe ke iska baatin achchha hai."
2642,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se aik janaaza guzra to logon ne us maiyat ki tareef ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''waajib ho gaii'' phir doosra janaaza guzra to logon ne uski burai ki, ya uske siwa aur alfaz (usi mafhoom ko ada karne ke liye) kahey (raawii ko shuba hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par bhi farmaya ''waajib ho gaii'' arz kya gaya. ya Rasulullah! aap ne us janaaze ke mutaalliq bhi farmaya ke wajib ho gaee aur pahley janaaze par bhi yahi farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya'' eman wali qaum ki gawahi (baargaahe-Ilaahii mein maqbool hai) ye log zameen par Allah ke gawah hain.''"
2643,"main Madina aaya to yahan wabaa phailii hui thi, log badi tezi se mar rahe they. main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein tha ke aik janaaza guzraa. logon ne us maiyat ki tareef ki to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke wajib ho gaee. phir doosra guzaar logon ne uski bhi tareef ki umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha wajib ho gaee. phir tesraa guzra to logon ne uski burai ki, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne uske liye yahi kaha ke wajib ho gaee. maine puchha ameerul-momineen! kya wajib ho gaee. unhon-ne kaha ke maine isi tarah kaha hai jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jis musalman ke liye char aadmi achai ki gawahi de dein usey Allah Taala jannat mein dakhil karta hai. ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha aur agar teen dein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke teen par bhii. ham ne puchha aur agar 2 aadmi gawahi dein ? farmaya 2 par bhii. phir ham ne aik ke mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi poochha."
2644,( parde ka hukm nazil honey ke baad) Aflah (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se (ghar mein aaney ki) ijazat chahi to maine unko ijazat nahi di. wo boley ke aap mujh se parda karti hain halanke main aap ka (doodh k rishtey se) chacha hun. maine kaha ke ye kaisey? to unhon-ne bataya ke mere bhai (Waayel) ki aurat ne aapko mere bhai ka hi doodh pilaya tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir maine iske mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aflah ne sach kaha hai. unhein (andar aaney ki) ijazat de diya karo (unse parda nahi hai).
2645,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi ke mutaalliq farmaya ''ye mere liye halal nahi ho saktiin, jo rishtey nasb ki wjah se haram ho jatey hain, wahi doodh ki wjah se bhi haram ho jatey hain. ye to mere dudh-sharik (doodh-shareek) bhai ki ladki hai.''"
2646,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan tashrif farma they. Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne aik sahabi ki awaz suni jo ( Ummul-Momenin ( Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein aaney ki ijazat chahta tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke maine kaha, ya Rasulullah ! mera khayal hai ye Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik chacha hain. unhon-ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! ye sahabi aap ke ghar mein (jis mein Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) rehti hain) aaney ki ijazat maang rahe hain. unhon-ne bayan kya ke aap ne farmaya, mera khayal hai ye falan saahib, Hafsa ke dudh-sharik chacha hain. phir Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi apne aik dudh-sharik chacha ke mutaalliq puchha ke agar falan zinda hotey to kya wo be-hijaab mere paas aa saktey they? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya'' haan! doodh se bhi wo tamam rishtey haram ho jatey hain jo nasb ki wjah se haram hotey hain.''"
2647,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ghar mein) tashrif laey to mere yahan aik sahib (unke dudh-sharik bhai ( baithey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, Aaisha ! ye kon hai? maine arz kya ke ye mera dudh-sharik bhai hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Aaisha ! zara dekh bhaal kar lo, kon tumhara dudh-sharik bhai hai. kyonke razaat wahi moa'tabar hai jo kam-umrii mein ho, Muhammad-bin-Kaseer ke sath us hadis ko Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Sufiyan Sory se riwayat kya hai."
2648,aik aurat ne fateh Makka par chori kar li thi. phir usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kya gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm ke mutabiq uska hath kaat diya gaya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir unhon-ne achi tarah tauba kar li aur shadi kar li. iske baad wo aati thin to main unki zarurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kar diya karti thi.
2649,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon ke liye jo shadi shuda na hon aur zina karein. ye hukm diya tha ke unhein so kode lagaey jayen aur aik saal ke liye jalaa watan kar diya jaey.
2650,"meri maan ne mere bap se mujhey aik cheez hiba dene ke liye kaha (pahley to unhon-ne inkar kya kyonke dusri biwi ke bhi aulad thi) phir razi ho gaey aur mujhey wo cheez hiba kar di. lekin maan ne kaha ke jab tak aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us maamle mein gawah na banaaein main is par razi na hongii. chunanche walid mera hath pakad kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. main abhi nai umr ka tha. unhon-ne arz kya ke us ladkey ki maan Umra-bint-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se aik cheez usey hiba karne ke liye keh rahi hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya iske ilawa aur bhi tumharey ladkey hain? unhon-ne kaha haan, hain. Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) ! ne bayan kya, mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya '' to mujh ko zulm ki baat par gawah na banaa.'' aur abu-Hareez ne Shabi se ye naql kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main zulm ki baat par gawah nahi bantaa.''"
2651,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein sabse behtar mere zamane ke log ( sahaba ( hain. phir wo log jo unke baad aaeingey ( Tabe-een ( phir wo log jo iske bhi baad aaeingey. ( tabba' Tabe-een ( Imran ne bayan kya ke main nahi janta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 zamanon ka (apne baad) zikr farmaya ya teen ka phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey baad aisey log paida hongey jo chor hongey, jin mein dayaanat ka naam na hoga. unse gawahi dene ke liye nahi kaha jaeyga lekin wo gawahiyan detey phirengey. nazrein maanengey lekin poori nahi karengey. mutaapaa unmein aam hoga.''"
2652,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse behtar mere zamane ke log hain, phir wo log jo iske baad hongey, phir wo log jo iske baad hongey aur uske baad aisey logon ka zamana aayega jo qism se pahley gawahi dengey aur gawahi se pahley qism khaaengey. ''Ibraaheem Nakhai (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne bayan kya ke hamarey badey buzurg shahadat aur ahad ka lafz zaban se nikalney par hamein maartey they."
2653,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kabeera gunahon ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik thehrana , maan-baap ki nafarmani karnaa, kisi ki jaan lena aur jhooti gawahi denaa.'' is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) ghandar , abu-Aamir , Behaz aur Abdus-Samad ne Shoba se ki hai."
2654,"main tum logon ko sabse badey gunah na bataaoon? teen baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah farmaya, sahaba ne arz kya, haan ya Rasulullah! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah ka kisi ko Sharik thehrana , maan-baap ki nafarmani karnaa, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tak tek lagaey huey they lekin ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) seedhey baith gaey aur farmaya, haan aur jhooti gawahi bhii. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us jumley ko itni martaba dohraya ke ham kehney lagey kash! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho jatey. Ismail bin Ibrahim ne bayan kya, unse Jurairi ne bayan kya, aur unse Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya."
2655,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko masjid mein Quran padhtey suna to farmaya ke un par Allah Taala raham farmaai mujhey unhon-ne us waqt falan aur falan aayatein yad dila diin jinhein main falan-falan Suraton mein se bhool gaya tha. Ibaad-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni riwayat main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ye alfaz zyada bayan kiye hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere ghar mein tahajjud ki Namaz padhi. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ibad (Raziallahu anhu) ki awaz suni ke wo masjid mein Namaz padh rahe hain. aap ne puchha Aaisha! kya ye Ibad ki awaz hai? maine kaha ji haan! aap ne farmaya, aey Allaah! Ibad par raham farmaa."
2656,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Bilaal (Raziallahu anhu) raat mein azan detey hain. isliye tum log sehrii kha pi saktey ho yahan tak ke (fajr ke liye) dusri azan pukaarii jaaey.'' ya (ye farmaya) yahan tak ke ''Abdullaah-ibne-umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan sun lo.'' Abdullaah-ibne-umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) naa-beenaa they aur jab tak unse kaha na jata subah ho gaee hai, wo azan nahi detey they."
2657,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan chand qubaaein aaiin to mujh se mere bap Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mere sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein chalo. mumkin hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unmein se koi mujhey bhi inayat farmaaein. mere walid (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar pahunch kar) darwazey par khadey ho gaey aur baatein karne lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki awaz pehchan li aur bahar tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik Quba bhi thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski khubiyan bayan karne lagey, aur farmaya ''maine ye tumharey hi liye alag kar rakhi thi, maine ye tumharey hi liye alag kar rakhi thii.''"
2658,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya aurat ki gawahi mard ki gawahi ke aadhey ke barabar nahi hai?'' ham ne arz kya kyon nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''yahii to unki aql ka nuqsan hai.''
2659,"unhon-ne umme-Yahyaa-binte-abii-Ahaab se shadi ki thi. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir aik siyah rang wali baandi aai aur kehney lagi ke maine tum donon ko doodh pilaya hai. maine iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri taraf se munh pher liya isliye main juda ho gaya. maine phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ja kar iska zikr kya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ab (nikaah) kaisey (baqi reh sakta hai) jabke tumhen us aurat ne bata diya hai ke usne tum donon ko doodh pilaya tha. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein umme-Yahyaa ko apne sath rakhney se mana farma diya."
2660,maine aik aurat se shadi ki thi. phir aik aurat aai aur kehney lagi ke maine tum donon ko doodh pilaya tha. isliye main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tumhen bata diya gaya (ke aik hi aurat tum donon ki doodh Sharik maan hai) to phir ab aur kya sura ho sakti hai apni biwi ko apne se juda kar de.'' ya isi tarah ke alfaz Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaaey.
2661,"wo qissa bayan kya jab tohmat lagaaney walon ne un par tohmat lagai lekin Allah Taala ne khud unhein us se barii qarar diya. Zohri ne bayan kya (ke Zohri se bayan karne waale, jinki sanad mein Zohri ke baad zikr hai) tamam rawiyon ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki us hadis ka eik-eik hissey bayan kya tha, kuchh rawiyon ko kuchh doosrey rawiyon se hadis zyada yad thi aur wo bayan bhi zyada behtar tareeqe par kar saktey they. bahar-haal un sab rawiyon se maine ye hadis poori tarah mehfooz kar li thi jisey wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey they. un rawiyon mein har aik ki riwayat se doosrey rawi ki tasdeeq hoti thi. unka bayan tha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar mein janey ka irada kartey to apni beeviyon ke darmyan Qura daaltey. jiske naam ka Qura nikaltaa, safar mein wahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jati. chunanche aik jang ke mauqe par, jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi shirkat kar rahe they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Qura dalwaayaa aur mera naam niklaa. ab main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath thi. ye waqia pardey ki aayat ke nazil honey ke baad ka hai. khair main aik hodaj mein sawar rehti thi, usi mein baithey-baithey mujh ko utara jata tha. is tarah ham chaltey rahe. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jihad se farigh ho kar wapas huey aur ham Madina ke qareeb pahunch gaey to aik raat aap ne kooch ka hukm diya. main ye hukm suntey hi uthi aur lashkar se aagey badh gaee. jab haajat se farigh hui to kajaawey ke paas aa gaee. wahan pahunch kar jo maine apna Sina tatolaa to mera zifaar ke kaley nageenon ka haar maujood nahi tha. isliye main wahan dobara pahunchi (jahaan qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye gaee thi) aur maine haar ko talash kya. us talash mein der ho gaee. us waqt mein wo ashaab jo mujhey sawar karatey they, aaey aur mera hodaj utha kar mere oont par rakh diya. wo yahi samjhey ke main usmein baithi hun. un dinon auratein halki phulkii hoti thin, bhari bhar kam nahi. gosht unmein zyada nahi rehta tha kyonke bahut maamooli ghizaa khaatii thin. isliye un logon ne jab hodaj ko uthaya to unhein iske bojh mein koi farq malum nahi hua. mein yun bhi nau-umr ladki thi. chunanche ashaab ne oont ko haank diya aur khud bhi uske sath chalney lagey. jab lashkar rawaana ho chuka to mujhey apna haar mila aur main padao ki jagah aai. lekin wahan koi aadmi maujood na tha. isliye main us jagah gaee jahan pahley mera qiyam tha. mera khayal tha ke jab wo log mujhey nahi paaengey to yahin lot ke aaeingey. Mina (apni jagah pahunch kar) main yun hi baithi hui thi ke meri aankh lag gaee aur main so gaee. Safwaan-bin-Muattal (Raziallahu anhu) jo pahley Sulami they phir zakwaanii ho gaey lashkar ke peechhey they (jo lashkariyon ki giri padi chizon ko utha kar unhein uske Malik tak pahunchaney ki khidmat ke liye muqarrar they) wo meri taraf se guzrey to aik soey huey insan ka saaya nazar padaa isliye aur qareeb pahunchey. parde ke hukm se pahley wo mujhey dekh chukey they. unke (inna-lillah) padhney se main bedaar ho gaee. aakhir unhon-ne apna oont bithaya aur uske agley paon ko mod diya (taake bila kisi madad ke main khud Sawar ho sakoon) chunanche main Sawar ho gaee, ab wo oont par mujhey bithaaey huey khud uske aagey-aagey chalney lagey. isi tarah ham jab lashkar ke qareeb pahunchey to log bhari do-pahar mein aaraam ke liye padao daal chukey they. (itni hi baat thi jiski buniyad par) jisey halaak hona tha wo halaak hua aur tohmat ke mamley mein pesh-pesh Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii-ibn-Salool (munaafiq) tha. phir ham Madina mein aagey aur main aik mahiney tak bimar rahi. tohmat lagaaney walon ki baton ka khub charcha ho raha tha. apni us bimari ke doran mujhey us se bhi bada shuba hota tha ke un dinon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wo lutf w karam bhi main nahi dekhti thi jinka mushaahida apni pichhli beemaariyon mein kar chuki thi. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar mein jab aatey to salam kartey aur sirf itna malum farma letey, mizaaj kaisa hai? jo baatein tohmat lagaaney waley phaila rahe they unmein se koi baat mujhey malum nahi thi. jab meri sihat kuchh theek hui to (eik raat) main umme-mistah ke sath manase ki taraf gaee. ye hamari qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki jagah thi, ham yahan sirf raat hi mein aatey they. ye us zamana ki baat hai jab abhi hamarey gharon ke qareeb baitul-khala nahi baney they. maidan mein janey ke silsiley mein (qazaaey haajat ke liye) hamara tarze-amal puraaney Arab ki tarah tha, main aur umme-Mistah-bint-abii-Raham chal rahi thi ke wo apni chadar mein ulajh kar gir padiin aur unki zaban se nikal gaya, mistah barbad ho. maine kaha, buri baat aap ne apni zaban se nikaalii, aisey shakhs ko bura keh rahi hain aap, jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik tha, wo kehney lagiin, aey bholii-bhaalii! jo kuchh un sab ne kaha hai wo aap ne nahi suna, phir unhon-ne tohmat lagaaney walon ki saari baatein sunain aur un baton ko sun kar meri bimari aur badh gaee. main jab apne ghar wapas hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey aur malum farmaya, mizaaj kaisa hai? maine arz kya ke aap mujhey waalidain ke yahan janey ki ijazat dijiye. us waqt mera irada ye tha ke unse us khabar ki tahqeeq karoongii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey janey ki ijazat de di aur main jab ghar aai to maine apni walida (umme- roomaan) se un baton ke mutaalliq poochha, jo logon mein phailii hui thin. Mina unhon-ne farmaya, betii! is tarah ki baton ki parwah na kar, Allah ki qism ! shayad hi aisa ho ke tujh jaisi Husain w khoobsurat aurat kisi mard ke ghar mein ho aur uski saukanein bhi hon, phir bhi is tarah ki baatein na phailaaii jaya karein. maine kaha Subhan-Allah ! ( sokanon ka kya zikr ( wo to doosrey log is tarah ki baatein kar rahe hain. unhon-ne bayan kya ke wo raat maine wahin guzaarii, subah tak mere aansu nahi thamtey they aur na neend aai. subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni biwi ko juda karne ke silsiley mein mashwara karne ke liye Ali ibne- abii-Taalib aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulwaya . kyonke wahi (is silsiley mein) ab tak nahi aai thi. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko aap ki beeviyon se aap ki mohabbat ka ilm tha. isliye usi ke mutabiq mashwara diya aur kaha, aap ki biwi , ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qasam, ham unke mutaalliq khair ke siwa aur kuchh nahi jaantey. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala ne aap par koi tangi nahi ki hai, auratein unke siwa bhi bahut hain, baandi se bhi aap malum farma liijiye, wo sachchii baat bayan karengii. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya (jo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khas khaadima thi) aur malum farmaya, Barira ! kya tum ne Aaisha mein koi aisi cheez dekhi hai jis se tumhen shuba hua ho. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, nahi, us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos farmaya hai. maine unmein koi aisi cheez nahi dekhi jiska aib mein un par laga sakun . itni baat zaroor hai ke wo nau-umr ladki hain. aata goondh kar so jati hain phir bakri aati hai aur kha leti hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi din ( member par) khadey ho kar Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii-ibne-Salool ke barey mein madad chahi . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik aisey shakhs ke barey mein meri kon madad karega jiski azeeyat aur takleef dahii ka silsile ab meri biwi ke mamley tak pahunch chuka hai. Mina Allah ki qasam, apni biwi ke barey mein khair ke siwa aur koi cheez mujhey malum nahi. phir naam bhi us mamley mein unhon-ne aik aisey aadmi ka liya hai jiske mutaalliq bhi mein khair ke siwa aur kuchh nahi janta. khud mere ghar mein jab bhi wo aaey hain to mere sath hi aaey. (ye sun kar) Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism main aap ki madad karunga . agar wo shakhs ( jiske mutaalliq tohmat lagaaney ka aap ne irshad farmaya hai) Aus qabeele se hoga to ham uski gardan mar dengey (kyonke Sad (Raziallahu anhu) khud qabila Aus ke sardaar they) aur agar wo khazraj ka aadmi hua, to aap hamein hukm dein, jo bhi aap ka hukm hoga ham ta'meel karengey. iske baad Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey jo qabila khazraj ke sardaar they. halanke us se pahley ab tak bahut Saleh they. lekin us waqt ( Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat par) hamiiyat se ghussa ho gaey they aur (Sa'd bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se) kehney lagey rab ke dawaam w baqaa ki qasam! tum jhoot boltey ho, na tum usey qatl kar saktey ho aur na tumharey andar uski taqat hai. phir Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey (Sa'd bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha zaad bhai (aur kaha, Allah ki qism ! ham usey qatl kar dengey (agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hukm hua) koi shuba nahi reh jata ke tum bhi munafiq ho. kyonke munaafiqon ki tarafdaar kar rahe ho. is par Aus w khazraj donon qabeelon ke log uth khadey huey aur aagey badhney hi waley they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo abhi tak member par tashrif rakhtey they. member se utrey aur logon ko narm kya. ab sab log khamosh ho gaey aur aap bhi khamosh ho gaey. mein us din bhi roti rahi. na mere aansu thamtey they aur na neend aati thi phir mere paas mere maan-baap aaey. mein aik raat aur aik din se barabar roti rahi thi. aisa malum hota tha ke rotey-rotey mere dil ke tukdey ho jaengey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maan-baap mere paas baithey huey they ke aik Ansari aurat ne ijazat chahi aur maine unhein andar aaney ki ijazat de di aur wo mere sath baith kar roney lagiin . ham sab isi tarah they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey aur baith gaey. jis din se mere mutaalliq wo baatein kahi ja rahi thin jo kabhi nahi kahi gain thin. us din se mere paas aap nahi baithey they. Mina Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik mahiney tak intizar kartey rahe they. lekin mere mamley mein koi wahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil nahi hui thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tashahud padhi aur farmaya, Aaisha ! tumharey mutaalliq mujhey ye ye baatein malum huin. agar tum us mamley mein barii ho to Allah Taala bhi tumhari Bara't (Tauba) zahir kar dega aur agar tum ne gunah kya hai to Allah Taala se maghfirat chaho aur uske huzoor tauba karo ke banda jab apne gunah ka iqrar karke tauba karta hai to Allah Taala bhi uski tauba qabool karta hai. junhii Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni guftgu khatm ki, mere aansu is tarah khushk ho gaey ke ab aik qatra bhi mehsus nahi hota tha. maine apne bap se kaha ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mere mutaalliq kahey . lekin unhon-ne kaha, qism Allah ki ! mujhey nahi malum ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mujhey kya kehna chahiye maine apni maan se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo kuchh farmaya, iske mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap hi kuchh kahiye, unhon-ne bhi yahi farma diya ke qism Allah ki! mujhey malum nahi ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya kehna chahiye unhon-ne bayan kya ke main nau-umr ladki thi. Quran mujhey zyada yad nahi tha. maine kaha Allah gawah hai, mujhey malum hua ke aap logon ne bhi logon ki afawaah suni hain aur aap logon ke dilon mein wo baat baith gaee hai aur uski tasdeeq bhi aap log kar chukey hain, isliye ab agar main kahun ke main (is bohtan se) barii hun, aur Allah khub janta hai ke main waqei us se barii hun to aap log meri us mamley mein tasdeeq nahi karengey. lekin agar main ( gunah ko) apne zimma ley loon, halanke Allah Taala khub janta hai ke main us se barii hon, to aap log meri baat ki tasdeeq kar dengey. qism Allah ki! mein us waqt apni aur aap logon ki koi misal Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke walid ( Yaqoob (Alaihissalam) (ke siwa nahi paatii ke unhon-ne bhi farmaya thaa (فصبر جميل والله المستعان على ما تصفون) ''sabr hi behtar hai aur jo kuchh tum kehtey ho us mamley mein mera madadgaar Allah Taala hai''. iske baad bistar par maine apna rukh dusri taraf kar liya aur mujhey ummeed thi ke khud Allah Taala meri Bara't (Tauba) karega . lekin mera ye khayal kabhi na tha ke mere mutaalliq wahi nazil hogi. meri apni nazar mein haisiyat us se bahut maamooli thi ke Quran Majeed mein mere mutaalliq koi aayat nazil ho. haan mujhey itni ummeed zaroor thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi khuwab dekhengey jis mein Allah Taala mujhey barii farma dega. Mina Allah gawah hai ke abhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah se uthey bhi na they aur na us waqt ghar mein maujood koi bahar nikla tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil honey lagi aur) shiddat wahi se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jis tarah pasiney paseeney ho jaya kartey they wahi kaifiyat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ab bhi thi. pasiney ke qatrey motiyon ki tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jism Mubarak se girney lagey. halanke sardi ka mausam tha. jab wahi ka silsile khatm hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans rahe they aur sabse pahlaa kalima jo aap ki zaban Mubarak se nikla, wo ye tha aey Aaisha ! Allah ki hamd bayan karke usne tumhen barii qarar de diya hai. meri walida ne kaha beti ja , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ja kar khadi ho jaa. maine kaha, nahi qism Allah ki main aap ke paas ja kar khadi na hongi aur main to sirf Allah ki hamd w sana karoongii. Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai thii (إن الذين جاءوا بالإفك عصبة منكم‏)'' jin logon ne tohmat tarashi ki hai. wo tum hi mein se kuchh log hain ''. jab Allah Taala ne meri Bara't (Tauba) mein ye aayat nazil farmai to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo Mistah-bin-Asaasa (Raziallahu anhu) ke ikhraajaat qaraabat ki wjah se khud hi uthatey they kaha ke qism Allah ki ab main mistah par kabhi koi cheez kharch nahi karunga ke wo bhi Aaisha par tohmat lagaaney mein Sharik tha. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki ولا يأتل أولو al-Fazal منكم والسعة‏ إلى قوله ghafoor رحيم''tum mein se saahibe-fazal w saahibe-maal log qism na khaaein. Allah Taala ke irshad ghafoor aur Rahim tak '' abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah ki qism ! bas meri yahi khahish hai ke Allah Taala meri maghfirat kar de. chunanche mistah (Raziallahu anhu) ko jo aap pahley diya kartey they wo phir dene lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab binte-Jahash ( (Raziallahu anhu) Ummul-Momenin ( se bhi mere mutaalliq puchha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Zenab ! tum ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke mutaalliq ( kya janti ho? aur kya dekha hai? unhon-ne jawab diya main apne kaan aur apni aankh ki hifazat karti hun (ke jo cheez maine dekhi ho ya na suni ho wo aap se bayan karne lagoon ( Allah gawah hai ke maine unmein khair ke siwa aur kuchh nahi dekha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke yahi meri barabar ki thin, lekin Allah Taala ne unhein taqwa ki wjah se bacha liya. abu-Rabee' ne bayan kya ke ham se Fulaih ne bayan kya, unse Hisham-bin-Urwa ne, unse Urwa ne, unse Aaisha aur Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne usi hadis ki tarah . abu-Rabee' ne (doosri sanad mein) bayan kya ke ham se Fulaih ne bayan kya, unse Rabee bin abi Abdur-Rehman aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne aur unse Qasim-bin-Muhammad -bin-abi-Bakr ne usi hadis ki tarah ."
2662,"aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney doosrey shakhs ki tareef ki, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya afsos! tu ney apne sathi ki gardan kaat daalii. tu ney apne sathi ki gardan kaat daalii. kai martaba (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah farmaya) phir farmaya ke agar kisi ke liye apne kisi bhai ki tareef karni zaroori ho jaey to yun kahey ke main falan shakhs ko aisa samajhta hon, aagey Allah khub janta hai, main Allah ke samney kisi ko be-aeib nahi keh sakta. main samajhta hun wo aisa aisaa hai agar iska haal janta ho."
2663,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suna ke aik shakhs doosrey ki tareef kar raha tha aur mubaalghe se kaam ley raha tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum logon ne us shakhs ko halaak kar diya. uski pusht tod di.
2664,"Uhud ki ladai ke mauqe par wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney (jang par janey ke liye) pesh huey to unhein ijazat nahi milii, us waqt unki umr chaudah saal thi. phir Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par pesh huey to ijazat mil gaee. us waqt unki umr pandarah saal thi. Naafe ne bayan kya ke jab main Umar-bin-abdul-Azeez ke yahan unki khilafat ke zamaney mein gaya to maine unse ye hadis bayan ki to unhon-ne farmaya ke chhotey aur badey ke darmyan (pandarah saal hi ki) had hai. phir unhon-ne apne haakimon ko likha ke jis bachchey ki umr pandarah saal ki ho jaey (uska fauji wazeefa) baitul-maal se muqarrar kar dein."
2665,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har baligh par Jume' ke din ghusl wajib hai.''
2666,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis shakhs ne koi aisi qism khaaii jis mein wo jhoota tha, kisi musalman ka maal chheenney ke liye, to wo Allah Taala se is tarah milega ke Allah Taala is par ghazabnaak hoga.'' unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par ash'as-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah gawah hai, ye hadis mere hi mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmai thi. mera aik Yahudi se aik zameen ka jhagdaa tha. Yahudi mere haq ka inkar kar raha tha. isliye main usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya (kyonke main muddaii tha) ke gawahi pesh karna tumharey hi zimme hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya gawah to mere paas koi bhi nahi. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Yahudi se farmaya ''phir tum qism khaao.'' ash'as (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main bol padaa, ya Rasulullah! phir to ye qism kha lega aur mera maal Hazam kar jaeyga unhon-ne bayan kya ke isi waqia par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا ) ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur qasmon se maamooli poonjii khareedtey hain aakhir aayat tak. ''"
2667,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis shakhs ne koi aisi qism khaaii jis mein wo jhoota tha, kisi musalman ka maal chheenney ke liye, to wo Allah Taala se is tarah milega ke Allah Taala is par ghazabnaak hoga.'' unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par ash'as-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah gawah hai, ye hadis mere hi mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmai thi. mera aik Yahudi se aik zameen ka jhagdaa tha. Yahudi mere haq ka inkar kar raha tha. isliye main usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya (kyonke main muddaii tha) ke gawahi pesh karna tumharey hi zimme hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya gawah to mere paas koi bhi nahi. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Yahudi se farmaya ''phir tum qism khaao.'' ash'as (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main bol padaa, ya Rasulullah! phir to ye qism kha lega aur mera maal Hazam kar jaeyga unhon-ne bayan kya ke isi waqia par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا ) ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur qasmon se maamooli poonjii khareedtey hain aakhir aayat tak. ''"
2668,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne likha tha ''nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mudduaa-alaih ke liye qism khaney ka faisla kya tha.''
2669,"Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jo shakhs ( jhooti ( qism kisi ka maal hasil karne ke liye khaaeyga to Allah Taala se wo us haal mein milega ke Allah paak is par ghazabnaak hoga. iske baad Allah Taala ne (is hadis ki) tasdeeq ke liye ye aayat nazil farmaaii ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم‏ ) ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon se thodi poonjii khareedtey hain. ( azaabe-aleem)'' tak. phir Ash'as-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) hamari taraf tashrif laey aur poochhney lagey ke abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) tum se kon si hadis bayan kar rahe they. ham ne unki yahi hadis bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha ke unhon-ne sahi bayan ki, ye aayat mere hi barey mein nazil hui thi. mera aik shakhs se jhagdaa tha. ham apna muqaddima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas le gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ya tum 2 gawah laao, warna uski qism par faisla hoga. maine kaha ke (gawaah mere paas nahi hain lekin agar faisla uski qism par hua) phir to ye zaroor hi qism kha lega aur koi parwah na karega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar farmaya ''jo shakhs bhi kisi ka maal leney ke liye ( jhooti ( qism khaaey to Allah Taala se wo us haal mein milega ke wo is par ghazabnaak hoga.'' uski tasdeeq mein Allah Taala ne uper zikr ki gaee aayat nazil farmai thi, phir unhon-ne yahi aayat tilawat ki."
2670,"Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jo shakhs ( jhooti ( qism kisi ka maal hasil karne ke liye khaaeyga to Allah Taala se wo us haal mein milega ke Allah paak is par ghazabnaak hoga. iske baad Allah Taala ne (is hadis ki) tasdeeq ke liye ye aayat nazil farmaaii ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم‏ ) ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon se thodi poonjii khareedtey hain. ( azaabe-aleem)'' tak. phir Ash'as-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) hamari taraf tashrif laey aur poochhney lagey ke abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) tum se kon si hadis bayan kar rahe they. ham ne unki yahi hadis bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha ke unhon-ne sahi bayan ki, ye aayat mere hi barey mein nazil hui thi. mera aik shakhs se jhagdaa tha. ham apna muqaddima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas le gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ya tum 2 gawah laao, warna uski qism par faisla hoga. maine kaha ke (gawaah mere paas nahi hain lekin agar faisla uski qism par hua) phir to ye zaroor hi qism kha lega aur koi parwah na karega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar farmaya ''jo shakhs bhi kisi ka maal leney ke liye ( jhooti ( qism khaaey to Allah Taala se wo us haal mein milega ke wo is par ghazabnaak hoga.'' uski tasdeeq mein Allah Taala ne uper zikr ki gaee aayat nazil farmai thi, phir unhon-ne yahi aayat tilawat ki."
2671,Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney apni biwi par Sharik bin Samahaa ke sath tohmat lagai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''is par gawah la warna tumhari peeth par had lagai jaaeygii.'' unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah! kya ham mein se koi shakhs agar apni aurat par kisi doosrey ko dekhega to gawah dhoondney daudega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barabar yahi farmatey rahe'' gawah la warna tumhari peeth par had lagai jaaeygii.'' phir liaan ki hadis ka zikr kya.
2672,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''teen tarah ke log aisey hain ke Allah Taala unse baat bhi na karega na unki taraf nazar utha kar dekhega aur na unhein paak karega balke unhein sakht dardnak azab hoga. aik wo shakhs jo safar mein zarurat se zyada pani ley ja raha hai aur kisi musaafir ko (jisey pani ki zarurat ho) na de. doosra wo shakhs jo kisi (musalmaanon ke liye bahut meharbaan) se bait karey aur sirf duniya ke liye bait karey ke jisse us ne bait ki agar wo uska maqsad pura kar de to ye bhi wafaadaarii se kaam ley, warna iske sath bait w Uhud ke khilaf kare. tesraa wo shakhs jo kisi se Asr ke baad kisi saman ka bhaaw karey aur Allah ki qism kha ley ke usey iska itnaa-itnaa rupya mil raha tha aur khareedaar us saman ko (iski qism ki wjah se) ley-ley. halanke wo jhoota hai.''"
2673,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs qism isliye khata hai taake iske zariey kisi ka maal (naajaaiz taur par) Hazam kar jaey to wo Allah se us haal mein milega ke Allah paak is par sakht ghazabnaak hoga.''
2674,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand aadmiyon se qism khaney ke liye kaha (eik aisey muqaddmey mein jiske ye log mudduaa-alaih they) qism ke liye sab aik sath aagey badhey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ''qasam khaney ke liye unmein aapasii Qura daala jaey ke pahley kon qism khaaey.''
2675,"aik shakhs ne apna saman dikhaa kar Allah ki qism khaaii ke usey us saman ka itna rupya mil raha tha, halanke itna nahi mil raha tha. is par ye aayat nazil hui ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke zariey thodi qeemat hasil kartey hain.'' ibne-abii-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke gaahakon ko phaansney ke liye dhokhadhadi se maal bechnewaalaa sood khor ki tarah khaain hai."
2676,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs jhooti qism isliye khaaey ke iske zariey kisi ka maal ley sakey, ya unhon-ne yun bayan kya ke apne bhai ka maal ley sakey to wo Allah Taala se us haal mein milega ke wo is par ghazabnaak hoga. Allah Taala ne isi ki tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil farmai ke) إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni ( jhooti ( qasmon ke zariey maamooli poonjii hasil kartey hain.''   phir mujh se Ash'as (Raziallahu anhu) ki mulaqat hui to unhon-ne puchha ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne aaj tum logon se kya hadis bayan ki thi. maine unse bayan kar di to aap ne farmaya ke ye aayat mere hi waqiey ke silsiley mein nazil hui thi."
2677,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs jhooti qism isliye khaaey ke iske zariey kisi ka maal ley sakey, ya unhon-ne yun bayan kya ke apne bhai ka maal ley sakey to wo Allah Taala se us haal mein milega ke wo is par ghazabnaak hoga. Allah Taala ne isi ki tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil farmai ke) إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni ( jhooti ( qasmon ke zariey maamooli poonjii hasil kartey hain.''   phir mujh se Ash'as (Raziallahu anhu) ki mulaqat hui to unhon-ne puchha ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne aaj tum logon se kya hadis bayan ki thi. maine unse bayan kar di to aap ne farmaya ke ye aayat mere hi waqiey ke silsiley mein nazil hui thii."
2678,"aik sahib (Zamaam-bin-Solba) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur Islam ke mutaalliq poochhney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''din aur raat mein panch namazein ada karnaa.'' us ne puchha kya iske ilawa bhi mujh par kuchh Namaz aur zaroori hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''nahin ye dusri baat hai ke tum nafl padho.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aur Ramazan ke rozey hain.'' us ne puchha kya iske ilawa bhi mujh par kuchh (rozey) wajib hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi ''siwaaey uske jo tum apne taur par nafl rakho.'' Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unke samney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zakat ka bhi zikr kya to unhon-ne poochha, kya (jo farz zakat aap ne batai hai) iske ilawa bhi mujh par koi khairat wajib hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''nahin, siwaey iske jo tum khud apni taraf se nafl do.'' iske baad wo sahib ye kehtey huey janey lagey ke Allah gawah hai na main inmein koi zyadti karunga aur na koi kamii. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar us ne sach kaha hai to kaamyaab hua.''"
2679,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar kisi ko qism khaani hi hai to Allah Taala hi ki qism khaaey, warna khamosh rahe.''"
2680,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum log mere yahan apne muqaddamaat latey ho aur kabhi aisa hota hai ke aik tum mein doosrey se daleel bayan karne mein badh kar hota hai (quwwate-bayaaniya badh kar rakhta hai) phir main usko agar iske bhai ka haq (ghalatii se) dila dun, to wo halal (na samjhey) usko na ley, main usko dozakh ka aik tukda dila raha hoon.''"
2681,"Hiraql ne unse kaha tha ke maine tum se puchha tha ke wo (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) tumhen kis baat ka hukm detey hain to tum ne bataya ke wo tumhen namaaz, sachchaaii, iffat, ahad ke pura karne aur amanat ke ada karne ka hukm detey hain. aur ye Nabi ki sifaat hain."
2682,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''munaafiq ki teen nishaniyan hain. jab baat kahe to jhoot kahii, amanat di gaee to usne usmein khayanat ki aur wada kya to usey pura nahi kya.''"
2683,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas (Bahreen ke aamil) Alaa-bin-Hizramii (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se maal aaya Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne elaan kara diya ke jis kisi ka bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par koi qarz ho, ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka us se wada ho to wo hamarey paas aaey. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par maine unse kaha ke mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wada farmaya tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itna maal mujhey ata farmaaengey. chunanche Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne teen martaba apne hath badhaatey aur mere hath par panch so, phir panch so aur phir panch so gin diye."
2684,"Hairaa ke Yahudi ne mujh se poochha, Musa (Alaihissalam) ne (apne mehar ke ada karne mein) kon si muddat poori ki thi? (yani aath (8) saal ki ya das saal ki, jinka Quran mein zikr hai) maine kaha ke mujhey malum nahi, haan! Arab ke badey aalim ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar poochh loon (to phir tumhen bata doonga) chunanche maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke aap ne badi muddat poori ki (das saal ki) jo donon muddaton mein behtar thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi jab kisi se wada kartey to pura kartey they."
2685,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, aey musalmaanon! ahle-kitab se kyon sawalat kartey ho. halanke tumhari kitab jo tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil hui hai, Allah Taala ki taraf se sabse baad mein nazil hui hai. tum usey padhtey ho aur is mein kisi qism ki aamezish (milawat) bhi nahi hui hai. Allah Taala to tumhen pahley hi bata chuka hai ke ahle-kitab ne is kitab ko badal diya, jo Allah Taala ne unhein di thi aur khud hi usmein badlaaw kar diya aur phir kehney lagey ye kitabullah ki taraf se hai. unka maqsad us se sirf ye tha ke is tarah thodi poojii ( duniya ki) hasil kar sakein to kya jo ilm (Qur'aan) tumharey paas aaya hai wo tum ko un (ahale-kitaab se poochhney ko nahi roktaa. Allah ki qasam! ham ne unke kisi aadmi ko kabhi nahi dekha ke wo un aayatein ke mutaalliq tum se poochhta ho jo tum par (tumhaarey Nabi ke zariie') nazil ki gaee hain."
2686,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ki hudood mein sustii baratney waley aur is mein mubtala ho janey waley ki misal aik aisi qaum ki si hai jisne aik kashtii (par safar karne ke liye jagah ke barey mein) Qura andazi ki. phir nateejey mein kuchh log nichey sawar huey aur kuchh oopar. nichey ke log pani lekar uper ki manzil se guzartey they aur us se uper walon ko takleef hoti thi. us khayal se nichey wala aik aadmi kulhaadii se kashtii ka nichey ka hissa kaatney laga (taake nichey hi samandar se pani ley liya karey) ab uper waley aaey aur kehney lagey ke ye kya kar rahe ho? usne kaha ke tum logon ko (mere uper aaney-jaaney se) takleef hoti thi aur mere liye bhi pani zaroori tha. ab agar unhon-ne nichey waley ka hath pakad liya to unhein bhi nijat di aur khud bhi nijat paaii. lekin agar usey yun hi chhod diya to unhein bhi halaak kya aur khud bhi halaak ho gaey.''
2687,"unki rishtedar aik aurat umme-Alaa naam ke ne jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait bhi ki thi, unhein khabar di ke Ansar ne muhajireen ko apne yahan thahraaney ke liye qurey daley to Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ka qiyam hamarey hissey mein aaya. umme-Alaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey ghar thahrey aur kuchh muddat baad wo bimar pad gaey. ham ne unki teemaardaarii ki magar kuchh din baad unki wafat ho gaee. jab ham unhein kafan de chukey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. maine kaha, Abu-Saaib ! (Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat ( tum par Allah ki rahmatein nazil hon, meri gawahi hai ke Allah Taala ne apne yahan tumhari zaroor izzat aur badaai ki hogi. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye baat tumhen kaisey malum ho gaee ke Allah Taala ne unki izzat aur badaai ki hogi. maine arz kya, mere maan aur bap aap par fidaa hon, mujhey ye baat kisi zariey se malum nahi hui hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Usman ka jahan tak mamla hai, to Allah gawah hai ke unki wafat ho chuki aur main unke barey mein Allah se khair hi ki ummeed rakhta hun, lekin Allah ki qasam! Allah ke rasool honey ke bawajud mujhey bhi ye ilm nahi ke unke sath kya mamla hoga. umme-Alaa (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagiin, Allah ki qasam! ab iske baad main kisi shakhs ki paakii kabhi bayan nahi karoongii. us se mujhey ranj bhi hua (ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney maine aik aisi baat kahi jiska mujhey haqiqi ilm nahi tha) unhon-ne kaha (eik din) main so rahi thi, maine khuwab mein Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye aik bahtaa hua chashma dekha. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khuwab bayan kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye unka amal ( nek ( tha."
2688,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar ka irada farmatey to apni beeviyon mein Qura andazi farmatey aur jiska naam nikal aataa, unhein apne sath ley jatey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye bhi mamool (routine) tha ke apni har biwi ke liye aik din aur aik raat muqarrar kar di thi. albatta Sauda-bintZam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apni umr ke aakhiri daur mein) apni baari Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko de di thi taake Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki unko raza hasil ho (is se bhi Qura andazi Sabit huii)."
2689,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar logon ko malum hota ke azan aur pahli saf mein kitna sawab hai aur phir (unhein iske hasil karne ke liye) Qura andazi karni padtii, to wo Qura andazi bhi kartey aur agar unhein malum ho jaey ke Namaz sawerey padhney mein kitna sawab hai to log aik doosrey se sabqat karne lagein aur agar unhein malum ho jaey ke isha aur subah ki kitni fazeelatein hain to agar ghutnon ke bal aana padta to phir bhi aatey.''"
